keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein is the originator of multiple financial transactions to Michelle's Transportation Company.
The transactions include amounts of $10,000, $20,000, $200,000, and $100,000.
All transactions were processed through Deutsche Bank Trust Company America.
The beneficiary of the transactions is consistently listed as Michelle's Transportation Company located on Little Saint James Island.
The document indicates a pattern of financial activity between Epstein and the transportation company over several years.
